summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Fourteenth Avenue Northwest from West 75th Street to West 80th Street et al, in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 19006, creating Local Improvement District No. 1814 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
